To upload the adruino code to the Arduino Pro Mini you will need to use the FTDI USB to TTL converter. This will require that you download the FTDI drivers. Link can be found below. 

https://ftdichip.com/drivers/d2xx-drivers/

The driver version used was the 2.12.28 but this is no longer supported. It can be found at the link above but newer version shoudl still work.
